Package froggerActors

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Actor
    Actor is the base class for all the interactive objects in the Frogger Game.
    Each interactive game object is known as an Actor.
    DryTurtle
    Represents the Red Turtle in Frogger Game.
    End
    Represents the destination Animal should reach to win the game.
    There are 3 types of End : an empty End, an End with a coin, an occupied End that has been reached by Animal.
    Log
    Represents the logs floating on the river in Frogger Game.
    2 types of logs : Log with bombs and Log without bombs.
    Monster
    Represents the Monster in the game.
    Obstacle
    Represents the Obstacles, which are the cars and the trucks on the road, in Frogger Game.
    Obstacle is also an Actor.
    Turtle
    Represents the turtles in Frogger Game
    The base class for Turtle
    WetTurtle
    Represents the Green Turtle in Frogger Game.
